              "settings": {
                "html": "<div class=\"idealson-hero-slider\">\n  <!-- Slide 1: Somnium Pillows -->\n  <div class=\"idealson-slide active\" data-slide=\"1\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #325a55 0%, #2a4a45 100%);\">\n    <div class=\"idealson-slide-content\">\n      <div class=\"idealson-grid\">\n        <div class=\"idealson-image-col\">\n          <div class=\"idealson-product-placeholder\">\n            <span>Заменить на реальное фото товара</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"idealson-text-col\">\n          <h2 class=\"idealson-title\">Просыпайся и сияй с Somnium!</h2>\n          <p class=\"idealson-description\">Глубокий сон — лёгкое утро. Попробуй заботу и комфорт!</p>\n          <a href=\"#pillows\" class=\"idealson-btn btn-primary\">Узнать больше о подушках</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <!-- Slide 2: Natural Beauty -->\n  <div class=\"idealson-slide\" data-slide=\"2\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7f7f7 0%, #ffffff 100%);\">\n    <div class=\"idealson-slide-content\">\n      <div class=\"idealson-grid\">\n        <div class=\"idealson-image-col\">\n          <div class=\"idealson-product-placeholder light\">\n            <span>Заменить на реальное фото товара</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"idealson-text-col\">\n          <h2 class=\"idealson-title dark\">Естественная красота — твой выбор</h2>\n          <p class=\"idealson-description dark\">Коллаген работает изнутри: кожа сияет, волосы крепче, ногти не ломаются</p>\n          <a href=\"#collagen\" class=\"idealson-btn btn-primary\">Выбрать вкус</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <!-- Slide 3: Pillow Quiz -->\n  <div class=\"idealson-slide\" data-slide=\"3\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7f7f7 0%, #ffffff 100%);\">\n    <div class=\"idealson-slide-content\">\n      <div class=\"idealson-grid\">\n        <div class=\"idealson-image-col\">\n          <div class=\"idealson-product-placeholder light\">\n            <span>Заменить на реальное фото товара</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"idealson-text-col\">\n          <h2 class=\"idealson-title dark\">Не знаете, какую подушку выбрать?</h2>\n          <p class=\"idealson-description dark\">Пройдите короткий тест и получите персональную рекомендацию</p>\n          <a href=\"#quiz-block\" class=\"idealson-btn btn-primary\">Пройти тест</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <!-- Slide 4: Weekly Promotion (Global Widget) -->\n  <div class=\"idealson-slide\" data-slide=\"4\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #aec958 0%, #9bb247 100%);\">\n    <div class=\"idealson-slide-content\">\n      <div class=\"idealson-grid\">\n        <div class=\"idealson-image-col\">\n          <div class=\"idealson-product-placeholder\">\n            <span>Заменить на реальное фото товара</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"idealson-text-col\">\n          <h2 class=\"idealson-title\">Акция недели</h2>\n          <p class=\"idealson-description idealson-promo-text\">Магний B6 в подарок: При покупке 1 кг банки натурального коллагена — МАГНИЙ B6 В ПОДАРОК</p>\n          <div class=\"idealson-promo-date\">Только с 28 мая по 1 июня</div>\n          <a href=\"https://wa.me/79999999999\" class=\"idealson-btn btn-outline idealson-promo-button\">Магний B6 в подарок</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <!-- Navigation -->\n  <div class=\"idealson-navigation\">\n    <button class=\"idealson-nav-btn prev\" onclick=\"idealsonPrevSlide()\" aria-label=\"Предыдущий слайд\">←</button>\n    <div class=\"idealson-dots\">\n      <button class=\"idealson-dot active\" onclick=\"idealsonGoToSlide(0)\" aria-label=\"Слайд 1\"></button>\n      <button class=\"idealson-dot\" onclick=\"idealsonGoToSlide(1)\" aria-label=\"Слайд 2\"></button>\n      <button class=\"idealson-dot\" onclick=\"idealsonGoToSlide(2)\" aria-label=\"Слайд 3\"></button>\n      <button class=\"idealson-dot\" onclick=\"idealsonGoToSlide(3)\" aria-label=\"Слайд 4\"></button>\n    </div>\n    <button class=\"idealson-nav-btn next\" onclick=\"idealsonNextSlide()\" aria-label=\"Следующий слайд\">→</button>\n  </div>\n  \n  <!-- Slide Counter -->\n  <div class=\"idealson-counter\">\n    <span id=\"idealson-current\">01</span> / <span id=\"idealson-total\">04</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\nlet idealsonCurrentSlide = 0;\nconst idealsonSlides = document.querySelectorAll('.idealson-slide');\nconst idealsonDots = document.querySelectorAll('.idealson-dot');\nconst idealsonCounter = document.getElementById('idealson-current');\n\nfunction idealsonShowSlide(index) {\n  // Hide all slides\n  idealsonSlides.forEach(slide => slide.classList.remove('active'));\n  idealsonDots.forEach(dot => dot.classList.remove('active'));\n  \n  // Show current slide\n  idealsonSlides[index].classList.add('active');\n  idealsonDots[index].classList.add('active');\n  \n  // Update counter\n  idealsonCounter.textContent = String(index + 1).padStart(2, '0');\n}\n\nfunction idealsonNextSlide() {\n  idealsonCurrentSlide = (idealsonCurrentSlide + 1) % idealsonSlides.length;\n  idealsonShowSlide(idealsonCurrentSlide);\n}\n\nfunction idealsonPrevSlide() {\n  idealsonCurrentSlide = (idealsonCurrentSlide - 1 + idealsonSlides.length) % idealsonSlides.length;\n  idealsonShowSlide(idealsonCurrentSlide);\n}\n\nfunction idealsonGoToSlide(index) {\n  idealsonCurrentSlide = index;\n  idealsonShowSlide(idealsonCurrentSlide);\n}\n\n// Auto-play slider\nsetInterval(idealsonNextSlide, 5000);\n</script>",
